Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.35,0:02:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起来吧\N一起来吧 一起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.35,0:02:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起来 一起来 一起来\N一起来 一起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.35,0:02:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次一起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.79,0:02:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,S．O．S!危险的放学后!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.20,0:02:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是莉采儿，干爹们请说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.70,0:02:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是干爹A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.33,0:02:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目标已在5分钟前通过，请说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.40,0:02:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是干爹B
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.67,0:02:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目标通过了，请说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.87,0:02:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是干爹C~\N无障碍物于会合地点~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.15,0:02:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照相机已经准备OK~\N请说~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.82,0:02:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收到!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.86,0:02:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿的作战 就在短短的\N千分之一秒之内结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.23,0:02:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，让我们重新\N看一次它的过程吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.97,0:02:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从莉采儿放出来的极细钢线以高速\N缠绕住脚踏车，拉近两者间的距离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.87,0:03:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接着在莉采儿噗通地\N坐上后座的瞬间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.21,0:03:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由干爹C利用超高感度的底片\N拍下了两人的合照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.32,0:03:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是莉采儿，进行得很顺利!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.79,0:03:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干爹，谢谢你们!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.36,0:03:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.10,0:03:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么一回事啊~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.10,0:03:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿~ 嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.64,0:03:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又在搞什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.57,0:03:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.71,0:03:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是说过别跟过来了吗~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.41,0:03:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?\N被缠住了耶，老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.85,0:03:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帐~ 这是什么啊~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.02,0:03:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这好像是叫什么“NASA”开发的\N很厉害的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.16,0:03:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样我想是没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.86,0:03:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎唷~ 才大清早的\N就这么恩爱啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.93,0:03:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少啰唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.07,0:04:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你，小葵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.37,0:04:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，解开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.00,0:04:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿嘿，第一次跟老公\N一起上学耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.41,0:04:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次一起上学?\N那是你自己跟过来的吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.88,0:04:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇~哇~第一次跟老公一起上学\N这样下去怎么行啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.25,0:04:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次一起上学了~成功了成功了~\N讨厌~达令你真是的 有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.65,0:04:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇~第一次一起上学!成功了!哇~\N莉采儿，你是我的什么人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.59,0:04:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妻子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.52,0:04:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然是妻子的话\N我的要求你听不听啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.86,0:04:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，什么我都听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.86,0:04:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.53,0:04:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.53,0:04:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有骗人吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.53,0:04:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯嗯嗯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.43,0:04:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那，去跟我以外的人交往吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.53,0:04:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.80,0:04:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要遵守约定喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.87,0:04:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.74,0:04:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.94,0:04:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙在想什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.01,0:04:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我该不会是被讨厌了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.18,0:04:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.01,0:04:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚刚在街上是我太心急了吗\N那种玩法...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.38,0:04:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玩...这讲法你是从哪学来的啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.39,0:04:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题的啦，那家伙嘴上那么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.32,0:04:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实他心里还是对莉采儿有感觉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.33,0:04:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那，是像这样活跳跳的感觉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.96,0:05:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活跳跳~活跳跳~\N呃，那我就不知道了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.40,0:05:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过身为他的儿时玩伴\N我的直觉是不会错的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.97,0:05:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.70,0:05:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的真的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.97,0:05:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.04,0:05:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.70,0:05:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的真的真的是真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.91,0:05:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就...就说不会错了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.71,0:05:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.48,0:05:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙就是太不懂得放弃了\N所以才没法对老师转移注意力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.08,0:05:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是笨蛋一个\N唷?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.15,0:05:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要试试真的\N去跟别的人交往啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.09,0:05:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙一定会追来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.15,0:05:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公会吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.72,0:05:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿的话一定没问题!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.59,0:05:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.59,0:05:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯~我应该跟谁交往看看呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.16,0:05:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗨，我钟爱的少女啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.93,0:05:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终于到了约定的周末了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.37,0:05:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.30,0:05:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我太高兴了\N今天，只属于我的天使终于要诞生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.94,0:05:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个，你是谁啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.44,0:05:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还真爱开玩笑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.11,0:05:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我啊，我凤凰院 龙之介啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.75,0:05:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初次见面，我叫岩城莉采儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.88,0:05:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初...初次见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.95,0:06:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初次见面!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.96,0:06:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了，没关系...\N反正我要的只有身体而已...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.09,0:06:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我再重邀一次吧\N今天放学后，可以陪我一下吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.13,0:06:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶?你是要跟我交往吗?\N当然啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.97,0:06:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了!要交往了，哇~哇~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.14,0:06:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能让你这么开心，我也很高...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.60,0:06:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那，就请你多多指教了~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.21,0:06:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兴呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.11,0:06:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀，岩城同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.65,0:06:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.72,0:06:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样好吗?莉采儿刚刚跟A班的\N凤凰院同学很要好似的回去了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那又怎样，又不关我的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.06,0:06:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，是吗?抱歉抱歉 拜拜罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.23,0:06:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.06,0:06:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说这次是他的本命...是指什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.63,0:06:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是说，凤凰院今天带回去的女孩\N恰好符合他喜欢的类型啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.00,0:06:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，那家伙好像有制作\N女孩子的裸体人像的癖好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.67,0:06:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不是还会收集女孩子的内裤吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.14,0:06:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说他研究过以后还出了同人志呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.08,0:07:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙那么有钱\N八成会让那女孩成为他的收藏品吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.82,0:07:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是把她脱光之后做成人像吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.19,0:07:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有可能有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.34,0:07:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厉害喔~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.34,0:07:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来玩猜打鬼一定很适合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.11,0:07:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然不是很懂，不过谢谢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.18,0:07:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来，请进吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.79,0:07:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可爱喔~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.69,0:07:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个也是...这个也是...还有那个...\N每个都好可爱喔~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.06,0:07:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有女孩子这么说，这还是第一次呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.37,0:07:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的好厉害呢，我好佩服你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.00,0:07:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是、是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.50,0:08:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一般人或许无法理解吧...\N小熊内裤其实是很具有浪漫气息的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.01,0:08:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就整个世界来看，小熊内裤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.81,0:08:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在许许多多的文献之中\N是以纯洁少女的象征被记载着的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.02,0:08:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯嗯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.15,0:08:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而，根据我的研究
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.09,0:08:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这件就是世界上最早诞生的小熊内裤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.82,0:08:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.53,0:08:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在1953年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.26,0:08:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由英国的金凯梅克伯爵\N特地为他的孙女所做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.03,0:08:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厉害喔~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.53,0:08:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,内裤上的小熊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.60,0:08:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕴含着大人们对遗忘的\N童年时的纯真所致的敬意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.74,0:08:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.75,0:08:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你果然是真正的天使啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.12,0:08:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.85,0:08:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请到这里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.36,0:08:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇!好厉害喔~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.99,0:08:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作品名是“12岁”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.90,0:08:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是你做的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.50,0:08:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.63,0:09:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信\N究极的天使就在12岁这时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.37,0:09:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既不属于大人，也不属于小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.14,0:09:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依然保持着赤子之心的存在...\N那就是12岁吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.14,0:09:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好像也是12岁呢~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.51,0:09:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，这个是不行的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.15,0:09:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这还不能算是真正的12岁\N这种东西只不过是膺品罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.88,0:09:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，就是你!\N你才是我所追求的真正的12岁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.65,0:09:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想要完成祂，那究极的天使!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.29,0:09:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了那个\N我需要你那12岁的身体...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.80,0:09:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来吧，乖乖屈服\N成为只属于我的人偶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.66,0:09:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要~!不要，不要啊~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.40,0:09:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会让你的美貌永远的维持下去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.81,0:09:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.81,0:09:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.64,0:09:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我无关...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.68,0:09:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来吧，把身上的衣服脱了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.15,0:09:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.82,0:09:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公，救我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.42,0:09:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁要理她啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.33,0:10:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿嘿，穿这个样子\N老公来接我的时候大概会吓一跳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.07,0:10:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等你很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.47,0:10:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也许会有些难受...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.70,0:10:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过没关系，很快就会结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.94,0:10:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿泳衣是要做什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.58,0:10:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了让你成为“天使”...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.72,0:10:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是无聊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.36,0:10:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太美了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.22,0:10:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成为我理想中的天使了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.86,0:10:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是什么人!?\N阻止他!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.23,0:10:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少啰唆~!我说让开就给我让开~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.37,0:10:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岩...岩城同学!你怎么突然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.60,0:10:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没什么突然不突然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.74,0:10:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉采儿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.24,0:10:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这家伙对莉采儿做了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.98,0:10:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做出这种事情\N你一点罪恶感也没有吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.88,0:10:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是有先取得她的同意的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.61,0:10:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪有可能啊?\N一定是你强迫她的吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.52,0:10:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的!她非常的高兴呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.22,0:11:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少来!普通人遭遇这种事\N会高兴的才会有鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.76,0:11:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然把莉采儿给做成人像\N给我变回来，你这混帐东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.23,0:11:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做成人像?你是不是搞错了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.90,0:11:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少跟我啰哩八唆的\N还不快把她给变回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.90,0:11:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你又怎样!擅自闯进人家家里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.27,0:11:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底你跟她是什么关系啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.50,0:11:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啰唆!莉采儿是我的“妻子”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.64,0:11:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了~第一次被老公承认耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.64,0:11:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你、为...为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.28,0:11:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.28,0:11:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还什么，人像啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.05,0:11:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是当了那个的“原型”啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.25,0:11:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耶!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.66,0:11:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先用好像果冻的橡胶把我的型取出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.79,0:11:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再费了一番功夫，就完成这个了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.03,0:11:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是老公第一次来接我耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.77,0:11:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要贴着我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.03,0:11:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞...搞错了，不好意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.31,0:11:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你，龙太郎同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.17,0:11:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是龙之介，我钟爱的少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.94,0:11:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天真的很高兴呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.28,0:12:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下啦，老公~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.28,0:12:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种心情还是第一次...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.82,0:12:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天，我有生以来第一次\N爱上了一位12岁的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.56,0:12:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然如此，不管用什么手段\N我都要将她夺过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.43,0:12:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就用我这双手，绝对要得到你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.47,0:12:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊~好舒服喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.20,0:12:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，拿浴巾来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.97,0:12:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你，老公\N你第一次为了我吃醋，我好高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.44,0:12:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁...谁吃醋啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.81,0:12:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可不要搞错了，笨蛋...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.73,0:12:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲啊\N冲啊 冲啊 老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.23,0:12:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲啊 冲啊\N冲啊 老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.50,0:13:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲啊 冲啊 冲啊\N老公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.01,0:13:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最喜欢你了 冲啊冲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.52,0:13:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男人和女人真是难以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.62,0:13:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了查清楚我去了图书馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.39,0:13:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然对比他年幼的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.39,0:13:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公是一点兴趣也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.77,0:13:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是人家好喜欢他\N所以我不会哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.51,0:13:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不气馁，不逃避\N更不会失去勇气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.78,0:13:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信总有一天春天会到来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.65,0:13:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿出认真的力量\N认真的力量向前冲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.16,0:13:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲啊\N冲啊 冲啊 老公啊
